{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Discover the new features in watchOS 26 and learn how to integrate them into your watchOS and iOS apps. Explore the ARM64 architecture, and dive into the new design system. We’ll also share updates for widgets and insights on how to bring controls to Apple Watch."}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2025\/334","isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Watch Video (20 min)"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc25-334-whats-new-in-watchos-26"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Related Sessions","anchor":"Related-Sessions"},{"type":"links","style":"list","items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-219-Meet-Liquid-Glass","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-361-Create-icons-with-Icon-Composer","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC24-10157-Extend-your-apps-controls-across-the-system","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC23-10043-Meet-MapKit-for-SwiftUI","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-278-Whats-new-in-widgets","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC22-10051-Go-further-with-Complications-in-WidgetKit","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-278-Whats-new-in-widgets"]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"What’s new in watchOS 26","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading"